               <p>JAMES PATTIE. I was going along the left-hand side of <placeName id="t18250915-45-crimeloc255">Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18250915-45-crimeloc255" type="placeName" value="Holborn"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18250915-45-crimeloc255" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-45-off253 t18250915-45-crimeloc255"></join>, towards Oxford-street, about nine o'clock on the evening of the 11th of September, and saw the prisoner, who touched me twice; he came to me a third time; I then put my hand to my pocket, and missed my handkerchief, which was safe about five minutes before; he was in the custody of a witness, who had the handkerchief in his hand.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250915-45-person354">
                  JESSE 
                  PHILLIPS
               <interp inst="t18250915-45-person354" type="surname" value="PHILLIPS"></interp>
