                     <interp inst="t18250915-45-person354" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in Holborn on Sunday last, and saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from the prosecutor's pocket; he threw it on the ground - I took it up, and took hold of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250915-45-person355">
                  DANIEL 
